    <body>
        <div class="note">
            <p class="Note-Text" MadCap:autonum="&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #bed230;&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatColor&quot;&gt;Note: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;">Deleting a Pulse user removes all access to Pulse. To give a user the ability to re-use the email address in Pulse, you must also delete the user from the dbo.Users and dbo.Login tables in the SQL&#160;Server instance for the Pulse database. Once the entries are deleted, the email can be used to create a new Pulse account.</p>
